  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下页面发布系统的完整流程。核心是从创建页面开始，经过隐私设置、发布时间配置，最后到渲染。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先把Pages子图搭建起来，包含创建编辑页、隐私设置、发布时间这几个节点。隐私设置那里用P2表示public/private两种状态，可以吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pages",
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。另外P3的published_at是可选的，没设置的话相当于立即发布。还有，页面内容是通过PageBlocks来添加的，这个步骤不能漏。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P3",
        "P5",
        "PageBlocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把P5加上，标注为Add Content Blocks via PageBlocks。现在Pages子图有P1到P5，还有P6负责渲染。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P5",
        "P6",
        "Pages"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "流程顺序是：创建后先设隐私，再设发布时间，然后才能添加内容块，最后渲染。但这里有个分支——侧边栏导航P4是optional的，它也能直接连到渲染。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P5",
        "P6",
        "P4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。P1→P2→P3→P5→P6是主线，P4单独出来连到P6。这样侧边栏导航确实不影响核心发布流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
